Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也脱离战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别有所保留, 把炮弹全部射光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,通过这个斜坡后就是海岸线了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,高度维持不变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是Valkyrie11
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,即将抵达海岸线
